# Module section titles (H2)

The app maps `##` headings to **section roles** for typography and layout (`js/lib/section-roles.js`). Keep these titles **exact** (case-insensitive) so styling applies:

| Role | Preferred `##` title |
|------|----------------------|
| Elevator | `## Elevator Pitch` |
| Discovery | `## Discovery Questions` |
| Objections | `## Objection Handling` |
| Technical deep | `## Technical Deep Dive [deep]` |
| Sales trio (tabs) | `## Overview` → `## Key Guidelines` → `## Common Pitfalls` → `## Process Deep Dive [deep]` |

**Sales trio modules** (`sales-rules-of-engagement`, `sales-process-and-salesforce`, `sales-operations-and-approvals`): the first three sections render as **tabs** when this order and titles match.

Unknown titles still render; they use the generic card style.
